review.comments: Listing description was 100% correct. The real situation was even better. The host has done very good job accommodating us and have done very good job writing necessary information on nearest shops and places to eat and visit . It was very easy to fallow and very useful at the beginning of our journey. The apartment was very clean and tidy, in particular want to underline the shower which is amazing start of the day. 5 min from the Metro and around 35 min walking from the city centre. All key museums are very close to apartments. Overall 10 out of 10. Happy to stay in apartment and the city as well.
